flowRoot.flowPara: To make the chair you should:
Use a [saw]{Qty: 1} to cut up six [planks of wood]{Qty: 6}.
Use 3.5 x 25mm wood screws. Remeber to drill a pilot hole with a [2mm drill bit]{Qty: 1}
